      <title>多姆布罗夫斯基说，特朗普贸易不确定性正在打击欧盟经济。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/trump-trade-uncertainty-is-hitting-eu-economy-dombrovskis-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟经济专员瓦尔迪斯·唐博罗夫斯基斯（Valdis Dombrovskis）表示，对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对欧盟打击欧盟的计划的贸易不确定性已经通过对欧盟进行投资的影响，这已经在影响集团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/trump-trade-uncertainty-is-hitting-eu-economy-dombrovskis-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 18:57:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉（Lula）敦促petrobras削减“抢劫”消费者的燃油经纪人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/petrobras-urged-by-lula-to-cut-fuel-brokers-who-rob-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达·席尔瓦（Luiz Inacio Lula Da Silva）周一说，巴西国营的石油生产商石油公司应该摆脱中介机构，直接向消费​​者出售，以降低燃油价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/petrobras-urged-by-lula-to-cut-fuel-brokers-who-rob-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 18:49:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
